%F A307930 a(n) = A129349(n)/2.
%e A307930 The sequence starts from a(2) because graph T(1) has no vertices.
%e A307930 a(2)=0 because graph T(2) is the singleton graph with no circuits.
%e A307930 a(3)=1 becaues graph T(3) is the cycle graph C3 with one circuit.
